elementor-element elementor-element-3fb9b3c elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3fb9b3c\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-cc88e83\" data-id=\"cc88e83\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8fa06ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8fa06ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Estimated Energy Requirement (EER)<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-c991400 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"c991400\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-b748f33\" data-id=\"b748f33\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e878a96 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e878a96\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Basics<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Estimated Energy Requirement (EER) Definition: Estimated Daily Calorie Requirement<\/li><li>*Indirect Calorimetry is Preferred Over EER if Available<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Adult EER<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Primary Requirements:<ul><li>Healthy: <strong>20-25 kcal\/kg\/d<\/strong><\/li><li>Critically Ill (Trauma, Surgery or Sepsis): <strong>25-30 kcal\/kg\/Day<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Burn Patients:<ul><li>Hypermetabolic State from Elevated Cortisol<\/li><li>Estimated EER = Normal EER + (30 x TBSA)<ul><li>TBSA: Total Burn Surface Area<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Morbidly Obese:<ul><li>Decreased Daily Requirements<\/li><li>BMI 30-50: 11-14 kcal\/kg\/d for Actual Body Weight<\/li><li>BMI &gt; 50: 22-25 kcal\/kg\/d for Ideal Body Weight<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Pediatric EER<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><strong>&lt; 6 Months: 110-120 kcal\/kg\/Day<\/strong><\/li><li>6-12 Months: 95-100 kcal\/kg\/Day<\/li><li>1-3 Years: 100 kcal\/kg\/Day<\/li><li>4-6 Years: 90 kcal\/kg\/Day<\/li><li>7-10 Years: 70 kcal\/kg\/Day<\/li><li>11-14 Years: 47-55 kcal\/kg\/Day<\/li><li>15-18 Years: 40-45 kcal\/kg\/Day<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-ebe662d elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"ebe662d\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-01a427b\" data-id=\"01a427b\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a671c94 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a671c94\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Macronutrient Requirements<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-4154636 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"4154636\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-93661ba\" data-id=\"93661ba\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-83e39d8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"83e39d8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Acceptable Macronutrient Distribution Ranges (AMDR)<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Carbohydrates: 45-65% (3-8 g\/kg\/Day)<\/li><li>Fat: 20-35% (0.5-1.5 g\/kg\/Day)<\/li><li>Protein: 10-35% (0.8-1.0 g\/kg\/Day)<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Calories Per Gram<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Fat: <strong>9<\/strong> kcal\/g<\/li><li>Protein: <strong>4 <\/strong>kcal\/g<\/li><li>Oral Carbohydrates: <strong>4 <\/strong>kcal\/g<\/li><li>Dextrose: <strong>3.4<\/strong> kcal\/g<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Ideal Body Weight (IBW)<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Men = 106 lb + 6 lb For Each Inch &gt; 5 ft<\/li><li>Women = 100 lb + 5 lb For Each Inch &gt; 5 ft<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Protein Requirements<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><strong>0.8-1.0 g\/kg\/Day<\/strong>: Well-Nourished<\/li><li>1.0-1.5 g\/kg\/Day: Malnourished<\/li><li>1.5-2.0 g\/kg\/Day: Postoperative Status, Sepsis or Trauma<\/li><li>2.0-2.5 g\/kg\/Day: Large Burns or Obese<ul><li>In Burns: Protein (g\/Day) = Normal Requirement + (3 x TBSA)<ul><li>TBSA: Total Burn Surface Area<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>*Decrease Rates in Patients with Renal Failure<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Nitrogen Requirements<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Give <strong>1 G<\/strong> Nitrogen Per <strong>Every 150 kcal<\/strong><\/li><li>There are Approximately <strong>6.25 g Protein for Every 1 g of Nitrogen<\/strong><ul><li>Nitrogen Requirements (g\/Day) = Protein Requirement \/ 6.25<\/li><li>Nitrogen Requirements (g\/Day) = Weight (kg) x 1 (Protein g\/kg\/day) \/ 6.25(Nitrogen g\/Protein g)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Fluids, Electrolytes &#038; Nutrition: Nutritional Requirements Estimated Energy Requirement (EER) Bas